{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"tokens":[{"text":"+ (","kind":"text"},{"text":"void","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:v"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"unregisterForPushNotifications:"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:v","text":"void"},{"text":" (^","kind":"text"},{"kind":"text","text":")("},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"NSError","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSError"},{"text":" * ","kind":"text"},{"text":"error","kind":"internalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":")) "},{"text":"completion","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}],"languages":["occ"]}]},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Block called when unregistration completes.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"Receives nil on success or an NSError on failure."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"completion"}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion","level":2,"type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Removes the device from receiving push notifications:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"orderedList","items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Notifies Pushwoosh servers to stop sending notifications to this device","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Removes the device token from Pushwoosh"}]}]}]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Use this when the user logs out, deletes their account, or explicitly disables notifications."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"Example","text":"Example"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Unregister during user logout:"}]},{"type":"codeListing","code":["class AuthenticationManager {","","    func logout(completion: @escaping (Result<Void, Error>) -> Void) {","        \/\/ Show loading indicator","        LoadingIndicator.show()","","        \/\/ First, unregister from push to stop receiving notifications for this user","        Pushwoosh.configure.unregisterForPushNotifications { [weak self] error in","            if let error = error {","                Logger.warning(\"Push unregistration failed: \\(error.localizedDescription)\")","                \/\/ Continue with logout even if unregistration fails","            }","","            \/\/ Clear user session","            self?.clearUserSession()","","            \/\/ Clear user tags","            Pushwoosh.configure.setTags([","                \"logged_in\": false,","                \"user_id\": NSNull(),","                \"email\": NSNull()","            ])","","            \/\/ Stop server communication if required by privacy policy","            if UserDefaults.standard.bool(forKey: \"clearDataOnLogout\") {","                Pushwoosh.configure.stopServerCommunication()","            }","","            LoadingIndicator.hide()","            completion(.success(()))","        }","    }","","    private func clearUserSession() {","        KeychainManager.shared.clearCredentials()","        UserDefaults.standard.removePersistentDomain(forName: Bundle.main.bundleIdentifier!)","        CoreDataManager.shared.clearUserData()","    }","}"],"syntax":"swift"}]}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/unregisterforpushnotifications:"]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration"]]},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/unregisterForPushNotifications:","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"sections":[],"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Unregisters the device from push notifications."}],"metadata":{"role":"symbol","title":"unregisterForPushNotifications:","symbolKind":"method","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"unregisterForPushNotifications:","kind":"identifier"}],"externalID":"c:objc(pl)PWConfiguration(cm)unregisterForPushNotifications:","modules":[{"name":"PushwooshCore"}],"fragments":[{"text":"+ ","kind":"text"},{"text":"unregisterForPushNotifications:","kind":"identifier"}],"roleHeading":"Type Method"},"kind":"symbol","references":{"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration/unregisterForPushNotifications:":{"url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/unregisterforpushnotifications:","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/unregisterForPushNotifications:","title":"unregisterForPushNotifications:","fragments":[{"text":"+ ","kind":"text"},{"text":"unregisterForPushNotifications:","kind":"identifier"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"unregisterForPushNotifications:","kind":"identifier"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Unregisters the device from push notifications."}],"role":"symbol"},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore":{"url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","type":"topic","title":"PushwooshCore","role":"collection","abstract":[{"text":"Core foundation module for Pushwoosh SDK.","type":"text"}],"kind":"symbol"},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration":{"type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration","kind":"symbol","title":"PWConfiguration","url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"PWConfiguration"}],"role":"symbol","abstract":[]}}}